workflow.name: Doctor appointment scheduler with Telegram, Gemini AI, and Google Sheets
workflow.description:
## AI Doctor‚Äôs Appointment Scheduler ‚Äì Process Flow

### User Interaction via Telegram:
The user sends a text or voice message through Telegram requesting a doctor‚Äôs appointment.

### Input Processing:
The AI agent receives and interprets the user‚Äôs message to identify the doctor‚Äôs name, preferred date, and time.

### Doctor Information Retrieval:
The agent accesses the doctor‚Äôs details stored in Google Sheets (or an Excel file).

### Schedule Verification:
It checks the doctor‚Äôs availability for the requested date and time using the doctor‚Äôs schedule ledger or database.

### Availability Response:
If the doctor is already booked, the agent informs the user and suggests alternative available slots.

If the doctor is available, the agent proceeds to confirm the appointment details with the user.

### Appointment Confirmation & Booking:
Once the user confirms, the agent records the appointment details in the Excel sheet (or Google Sheet).

### Confirmation Notification:
The agent sends a confirmation message to the user through Telegram, summarizing the appointment details (doctor name, date, and time).

parameters.content:
## Doctor‚Äôs Appointment Scheduler Agent
This intelligent assistant helps patients conveniently schedule doctor appointments through text or voice interaction.

 The agent retrieves doctor information stored in Google Sheets.

 It checks the doctor‚Äôs availability using the doctor‚Äôs schedule ledger tool.

 If the doctor is already booked for a specific date and time, the agent notifies   the user and suggests alternative slots.

 If the doctor is available, the agent confirms the appointment details with the user and books the slot for the selected date and time.

## Doctor_Info Tool Schema

Doctor name ,Department, 	Fees

## Doctor Schduler Schema

Doctor Name, 	Patient Name, 	Booked Date, 	Booked Time
